Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:05.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Iizuka was holding Manaka-san's \Nthings for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:07.74,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:10.55,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Sayu, you always say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.30,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:14.38,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.89,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.23,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:20.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:22.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sea slug's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Miuna-chan made it for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:34.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,so I wouldn't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't... lose it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:45.15,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The five years I've spent with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.65,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you that whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:50.95,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Living by the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,just as I've come \Nto understand the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:55.85,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm starting to \Nunderstand you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:01:03.34,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to know when you'll \Nget angry, laugh, and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:10.54,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that your feelings \Nare for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Did I understand wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.07,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If it was a misunderstanding, \NI'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:30.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:33.45,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:41.55,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't love you, Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.14,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:53.46,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,are lingering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.06,Episode-Title - Copy,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-Four:\NDetritus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.28,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Just five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.51,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The time I've spent with Tsumugu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.22,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,is just five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:11.50,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I've been with Hikari and the \Nothers ever since we were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:14.43,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.35,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Why just after five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.23,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.58,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.83,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.79,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to the guy you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.21,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,you get weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.29,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.43,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,tell me how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.09,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,If that'll help you feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.39,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.91,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.84,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I was always the odd man out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.90,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things didn't work \Nout with you and Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.76,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that it'd be \NTsumugu next and not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to love Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.70,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,If I fell in love with \Nanyone other than Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.29,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be betraying \Neveryone still sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:15.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,everyone whose time stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:16.62,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I love Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I made sure I wouldn't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.48,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I always made sure I didn't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:27.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,When Hikari came back, I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I was the only\None who became an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd see through me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.78,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,about various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But Hikari told me I hadn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.48,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I still loved Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.20,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.63,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We're all here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.71,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,We came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:03.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to \Nfool your own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.43,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka loves Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reawaken \NManaka's feelings of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept Tsumugu's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:19.81,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She does!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.69,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You're also as stubborn as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the sea again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.55,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-chan, are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.44,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.93,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:51.31,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Akira wrote a letter today at kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.31,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Would you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.85,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.73,I love Manaka,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I love Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:02.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"I love... Manaka"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.46,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Being his mom, I can't say\NI don't have mixed feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.60,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,but in a way, it sort \Nof makes me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.79,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you being all bashful for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.72,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Manaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:18.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.70,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:21.84,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:22.93,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.78,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! Don't worry, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.31,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:34.01,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you know your \Nname means "don't give up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.10,I love Manaka,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I love Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.16,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.38,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:06.23,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari is doing whatever \Nhe can to get Manaka-san's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.16,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,feelings back, no matter \Nhow much it hurts him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:12.06,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that I can do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.45,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka's pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.93,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a lot to thank you for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.93,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you hate to admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But you made a flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and we were able to go to\NShioshishio thanks to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't treat you like \Na little kid anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think I'll ever \Nbe able to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.20,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You're being rather honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.50,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.83,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.88,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if it's for Manaka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.54,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,you can even change your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:55.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Why do you have \Nto say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:09:00.59,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do for Hikari \Nwho has feelings for Manaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:10.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:14.82,Italics,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,...is to make sure that Hikari \Ndoesn't find out about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.63,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:21.70,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.59,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,A large serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to school early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Akari and Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.57,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were going \Nto kindergarten early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.10,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:45.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.71,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hii-kun. Who do you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.32,Main,hiari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking \Nabout all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what "love" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I love all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,but I get the feeling I \Ndon't really understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:10.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:11.93,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, it's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:15.63,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"That"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Things will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.51,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you know, things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.06,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The color in your face looks better today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.05,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:37.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay if I started \Nliving in a dorm next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I asked my instructor about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and apparently there's a dorm room open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.63,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care of the housing \Nfee with my part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:48.97,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.46,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,the story you were telling me about \Nthe Ojoshi-sama the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:04.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,After the Sea God took something \Nprecious from the Ojoshi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and she returned to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.72,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The man she loved was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:11.77,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:16.55,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,He went out to the sea to look \Nfor Ojoshi-sama and drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,A-And then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:23.12,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,There was no one waiting for Ojoshi-sama\N when she came back to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.08,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you headed home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.29,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.93,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,The red-bellied sea \Nslug is really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.09,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,"Red-bellied sea slug"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.75,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that replies if \Nyou tell it your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.96,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You really do know \Neverything about the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.93,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.28,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.24,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to you guys man-to-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Man-to-man"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.45,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Could you curse me one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:06.36,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:10.97,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,When people ask me to curse them, \NI really don't feel like doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:16.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You had us come with you \Nso you could say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.37,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:17.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:20.02,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If we offer an Ojoshi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:24.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I think the end of the \Nsurface will be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And Mukaido might get her feelings back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do the Ofunehiki and \NManaka have to do with—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.59,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Detritus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.67,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The dead bodies of plankton
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and the remains of other\Nmicroorganisms are floating in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it when my Ena awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:46.00,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The multitude of feelings that are floating \Nin the sea like detritus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.84,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,"Multitude of feelings"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Like what we heard\Nthe other day—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,all the Sea God's feelings\Nthat melted into the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.91,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the Sea God's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:13:01.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they were memories that \Nbelonged to the people who live in Shishio,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,or if they belonged \Nto the swimming fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Among the nameless, timeless feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.86,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a presence I knew very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.88,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure those were Mukaido's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.06,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.49,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Because Mukaido became the sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,the scatterings of the Sea God's feelings \Nand the sacred fire's will became one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.88,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and balance was established.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Then if we offer another sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:28.23,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't suggesting that \NManaka be a sacrifice again—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.24,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If it holds Mukaido's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.98,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If we put that onto \Na wooden Ojoshi-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.90,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't that serve as a \Nreplacement for Mukaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:42.18,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If the Sea God's feelings are led \Nto believe that Mukaido returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:45.55,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Mukaido's feelings that \Nwere taken may return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:48.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what you're \Nsaying one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's baseless and insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to at least give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.75,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What if we involve a whole \Nbunch of people like last time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and nothing comes out of it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:04.30,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's a \Npoint unless we struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.23,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:11.82,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You said something similar five \Nyears ago, did you not, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.32,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.33,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,How amusing. I shall lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:22.96,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,But an Ofunehiki done just by those \Non the surface is merely a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.46,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still all right with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:25.83,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.00,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to do something \Nthan nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:30.16,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.93,Request for Volunteers,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Request for Volunteers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.60,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing an Ofunehiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.97,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.83,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.59,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.04,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.78,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,This many people already showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.67,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been wanting to do the \NOfunehiki again all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.24,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Heyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.55,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hikari, you really still are a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.41,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, talk about a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Egawa-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:13.18,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,I brought my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:14.48,Main,wife,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.17,Main,wife,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for taking good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.74,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted everyone that left as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.81,Main,aki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.76,Main,shimizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.97,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.82,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sayama, hold that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.66,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Brash with people as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.24,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,This is all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,sort of nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.20,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fun, Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:49.59,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Is the wardrobe moving along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:57.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this will really work \Nin the place of the Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.27,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know if we don't try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:05.81,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka took the place of \NOjoshi-sama for five years
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:10.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,while I was on the surface, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.89,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Then this time, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.87,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Slacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.54,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.80,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You like Chisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:44.64,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You found me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.70,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.38,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:51.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You totally tried to act cool \Nand pretend it was nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.93,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,when you asked out \NChisaki-san, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently you heard \Nabout that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.59,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.93,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if she \Nrejected you or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.32,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,but why not attack this more head-on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.84,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:07.96,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,actually show her your pained \Nface like the one you just had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.92,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What good would that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.91,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,If she pities me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.43,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,with how Chisaki and I are right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:19.29,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be like Akari-san \Ncomforting Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.93,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be way too damaging to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.64,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I did actually think about \Nwhat would have happened
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:28.34,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,if I hadn't hibernated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.02,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think it \Nwould have mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:35.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki had some feelings for \NTsumugu five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.73,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,and I've always been the outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.88,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki's eyes are always looking \Nat someone other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:42.86,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.36,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop acting like the tragic heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.96,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,"Heroine"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.88,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, not the hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.13,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as Chisaki, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:51.99,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.71,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:57.88,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,always been watching you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.72,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.84,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,been watching you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.71,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,This whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:07.46,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.63,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was able to try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.65,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So you could have some balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.32,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So you wouldn't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:20.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,So you would see me as an actual girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.90,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Even while you were gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.79,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You were right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.24,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You were right here in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:43.73,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:44.50,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:49.52,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I was in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,In reality... I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.30,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,When I came back to the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.23,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari had Akari-san's family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,and Chisaki had Tsumugu's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:05.82,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:09.24,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,that no one was actually waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.23,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:13.97,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You are a kid after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.70,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.37,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Are you disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.16,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,that the big brother you \Nadmired is actually like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.22,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.34,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Should I give you a reply?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.14,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I know there's no chance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:32.90,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I had always been looking at Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.73,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.43,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'll actually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.83,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,start looking at you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.13,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Not as a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.91,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,but as a girl who's my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.10,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be okay if I started there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.08,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,About my future with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.36,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're so condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.33,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:01.50,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.19,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.01,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.43,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna head home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take Miuna \Nhome on your way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.56,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.58,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on \Nyou again tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,actually, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.24,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:30.78,Main,sayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't gone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:45.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The dawn is so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:48.75,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.88,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You seem down, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:55.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Since that day, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:59.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,a lot has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared that it might happen again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.84,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:05.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.40,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what will happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.42,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, I'm with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And being with everyone is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:18.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone that I'm in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.11,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.42,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.39,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get that feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:26.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.37,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that you love, Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:33.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Saying who you love isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.96,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.76,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no good, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand soon enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the Ofunehiki is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.97,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When the Ofunehiki is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:48.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the Ofunehiki a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:51.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wave that flag as hard as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.63,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Flag"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:54.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.59,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,I love Namaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.12,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I love Manaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:36.05,Main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:36.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:37.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:38.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.10,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty-Five: \NLove is Like the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:40.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Love is like the sea.
